metadata.name: Way home
metadata.description:
I really like trains - the measured sound of wheels calms and puts me in a meditative state. Outside the window, one landscape replaces another, and your thoughts are somewhere very far away...
On the way home, there is time to remember the past and dream about the future.

Artwork specs:
Seamless loop
2400x2400 px
Edition 1/1
MP4
